@lw394 Could you please let me know whether you are running on GPU or CPU?
tf.nn.moments is basically doing a parallel reduce_sum over the tensor, and on GPU it's quite possible that large reductions have non-deterministic floating point rounding errors.
@rmlarsen @zheng-xq  Do either of you know whether moments is expected/promised to be 100% deterministic?

